\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 Flip the Script\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Week 1 \'96 You\'92re not good enough!\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 ME\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 Joke about the graphic for bunnies stay dead!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you were a young Jewish boy there were really only two options in your future.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bate Say Fair\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bate \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  We\'92ve all been given a script like that before haven\'92t we?\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92ve had a teacher or coach tell us we couldn\'92t cut it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}A spouse who left us or cheated on us and made up feel unlovable\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}A child who said some stuff they can\'92t take back\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We all have conversation in our memory that have guided us to this very day.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The worst person to give us a negative script though is ourselves\'85when we beat ourselves up over what we\'92ve done or not done.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  In light of all this I want to look at a passage that I believe when understand the script they are walking around with it changes everything.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to pick up a story where Jesus had been teaching and he sitting on this guys boat and he says this to they guy who owns the boat.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When he had finished speaking, he said to Simon,\'a0\'93Put out into deep water, and let down the nets for a catch.\'94\

\f0\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Simon answered, \'93Master,\'a0we\'92ve worked hard all night and haven\'92t caught anything.\'a0But because you say so, I will let down the nets.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now wait, if Peter is fishing as a trade\'85what does that mean as far as his education?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That at some point someone told him\'85you can\'92t cut it\'85you\'92re not good enough\'85go home!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf4 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When they had done so, they caught such a large number of fish that their nets began to break.\'a0  Luke 5\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So Jesus shows up on the scene and does this incredible miracle!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in Matthew we read what Jesus says to him in response\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf4 \super 19\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub \'93Come, follow me,\'94\'a0Jesus said,\'a0\'93and I will send you out to fish for people.\'94\'a0
\f2\b \super 20\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub At once they left their nets and followed him.  Matthew 4\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in this moment his life is changed forever\'85because his script was flipped!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}See up to this point he had been told he wasn\'92t good enough\'85he couldn\'92t do it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But Jesus comes along and says to him\'85I think you can do what I do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I think you can cut it\'85you can be my disciple and carry my yoke.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In the church we talk all the time about how we need to believe in God but I don\'92t think we talk enough about how much God believes in us.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so Peter\'92s world is flipped upside and he just leaves everything and goes where his Rabi goes.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(I could sit here longer)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}BUT, if you\'92re here today and you grew up in the church you know that following God isn\'92t easy\'85in fact it is hard!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And just like us Peter messes up.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He fell through water (which in and of itself is normal, unless you go big like Peter and try and walk on water and then Jesus looks at you and asks why you doubted)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He asked Jesus if he should forgive someone 7 times and Jesus told him 7X70\'85yeah he was way off on that one!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You know what, it\'92s not in there but I\'92m sure at some point he told a white lie about something\'85maybe one of the disciples mom\'92s asked if she looked fat in the tunic and Peter told she look great\'85I don\'92t\'92 know but I\'92m sure he did something like that.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}At one point Jesus calls him Satan\'85not sure if you\'92re new to this whole religion thing but that\'92s pretty much the worse thing you can call someone in our book.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And then towards the end Jesus tells his disciples he is going to die and their response is to talk amongst themselves about who is the most awesome at their job!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now\'85the Satan one is pretty bad and the are ok\'85but there is one moment is Peter\'92s life that is defining for him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He denies his best friend.  Jesus tells him that he will deny Him and Peter still does it\'853 times!  It\'92s as if Jesus kept giving him opportunities to get it right and he couldn\'92t.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(expound here a little)\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve got one of those moments too right?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s a sin that is HUGE in your eyes.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It may or may not be a secret\'85it could be an addiction that is crippling in your life.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It could be something in your past you did and you can\'92t get over.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Many many people have at least one thing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And the problem is this one thing is so big in their eyes they can\'92t see past it.  (I need to be standing behind the Lego pile at this point)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  So what does Peter do?  He goes back\'85he retreats\'85he returns to the script that told him he couldn\'92t do it.  He becomes a fisherman again.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93I\'92m going out to fish,\'94 Simon Peter told them, and they said, \'93We\'92ll go with you.\'94 So they went out and got into the boat, but that night they caught nothing.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so there are people here today who\'92ve left the church, left God, or maybe even never went to God\'85all because you think God\'92s focused on how good of a person you are.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You believe the lie that you\'92re aren\'92t good enough!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So go backwards in life.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Early in the morning, Jesus stood on the shore, but the disciples did not realize that it was Jesus.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He said,\'a0\'93Throw your net on the right side of the boat and you will find some. \'94When they did, they were unable to haul the net in because of the large number of fish.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f3 \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sound familiar? \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s the same miracle!  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the only record we have of Jesus doing the same miracle.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Even when he healed people of the same disease he seemed to do it differently\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But here\'85It\'92s the same thing!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The question has to be asked\'85WHY?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why would Jesus do the same miracle to someone who already know he can do that miracle and also has just let you down in his biggest way.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  So Peter freaks out and realizes it is Jesus and swims to the shore only to find Jesus already has some fish and food ready and they have the conversation that ends with this\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0 \cf4 Then he said to him,\'a0\'93Follow me!\'94  John 21\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus, does the same miracle, to remind him of his calling and tell him he can\'92t mess it up!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of how we see sin and how God see\'92s sin\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are three types of people here today.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are good with God, and you either don\'92t have a big sin, don\'92t think you have a big sin, or you\'92ve made peace with it\'85I\'92m not talking to you today!  You\'92re fine!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You used to be close to God\'85but you\'92re Peter\'85you blew it or at least you think you did.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve never been close to God\'85and if this is you I\'92ve got good news and bad news.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re a great person\'85this is how God see\'92s your sin\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re a terrible person\'85this is how God see\'92s your sin\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s all the same\'85and the solution is all the same!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Next Steps\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Change how you see yourself and God and know that it takes you believing in God, but also you knowing God believes in you!\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}A belief that you are forgiven and loved more than you can imagine.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Give your life to Jesus.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(walk through this by knocking over the lego stands)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re going to wrap up today with a prayer.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And whether you already given your life to Christ or you need to for the first time, I believe all of us need to pray this prayer.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Whether it is to remind us of our calling and his belief in us, or for us to create a moment to start a journey with Him\'85either way I want us all to bow our heads and if you\'92re here today and your either a Christian or God is working in you and you need to make that commitment I want you to repeat after me.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 Prayer:\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Jesus, I know you love me.  I believe you lived a sinless life and died for my sins.  I believe you rose again 3 days later.  Today, no matter what my past is filled with, I\'92m committing to follow you!  Remove my sins, remove my guilt.  Help me be faithful.  Help me live out my calling to follow you!  Amen!\
}